\c 33
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli balaywa ukuthi basuke eSinayi
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Hamba wenyuke lapha wena labantu owabenyusa elizweni leGibhithe\x + 32.7.\x*, uye elizweni engalifungela uAbrahama, uIsaka loJakobe ngisithi: Inzalo yakho ngizayinika lona\x + Gen. 12.7; Eks. 32.13.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo ngizathuma ingilosi phambi kwakho\x + 32.34.\x*, ngixotshe amaKhanani, amaAmori, lamaHethi, lamaPerizi, amaHivi, lamaJebusi\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 3 Uye elizweni eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 3.8.\x*; ngoba kangiyikwenyuka phakathi kwakho\x + 33.15-17.\x*, ngoba uyisizwe esintamo lukhuni\x + 32.9.\x*, hlezi ngikuqede endleleni\x + 32.10. Nani 16.21,45.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kwathi abantu sebezwile lelilizwi elibi, balila\x + Nani 14.39.\x*; njalo kakulamuntu owafaka izigqizo zakhe\x + Hez. 24.17,23. 26.16.\x*;
\v 5 ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayithe kuMozisi: Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli \add uthi\add*: Lingabantu abantamo zilukhuni\x + 33.3.\x*; ngisenyuka ngiphakathi kwakho ngokucwayiza kwelihlo\x + Nani 16.21.\x*, ngizakuqeda\x + 32.12.\x*. Ngakho-ke khupha izigqizo zakho kuwe ukuze ngazi engizakwenza kuwe.
\v 6 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebezihlubula izigqizo zabo kusukela entabeni yeHorebe.
\s Ithente lenhlangano
\p
\v 7 UMozisi wasethatha ithente walimisa ngaphandle kwenkamba, khatshana lenkamba; walibiza ngokuthi lithente lenhlangano.\x + 29.42,43.\x* Kwasekusithi wonke odinga iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Lan. 16.10. Hlab. 40.16.\x* waphuma waya ethenteni lenhlangano elalingaphandle kwenkamba.
\v 8 Kwakusithi lapho uMozisi ephuma ukuya ethenteni, bonke abantu basukume, beme kube ngulowo lalowo emnyango wethente lakhe\x + Nani 16.27.\x*; bakhangele emva kukaMozisi aze angene ethenteni;
\v 9 njalo kwakusithi lapho uMozisi esengene ethenteni, insika yeyezi yehle\x + 13.21; Hlab. 99.7.\x*, ime emnyango wethente; ibisikhuluma loMozisi\x + 13.21, Hlab. 99.7.\x*.
\v 10 Lapho bonke abantu beyibona insika yeyezi imi emnyango wethente, bonke abantu basukume bakhonze\x + 4.31. 12.27. 34.8.\x*, kube ngulowo lalowo emnyango wethente lakhe.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma-ke kuMozisi ubuso ngobuso\x + Nani 12.8. Dute. 34.10. Gen. 32.30.\x*, njengomuntu ekhuluma lomngane wakhe. Wasebuyela enkambeni, kodwa uJoshuwa inceku yakhe\x + 17.9. 24.13. 32.17.\x*, indodana kaNuni, ijaha, kasukanga phakathi kwethente.
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* ithembisa ukuhamba loMozisi
\p
\v 12 UMozisi wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Khangela, uthi kimi: Yenyusa lababantu\x + 32.34.\x*; kodwa wena kawungazisanga ozamthuma lami. Kanti wena uthe: Ngiyakwazi ngebizo\x + 33.17.\x*, futhi uthole umusa emehlweni ami\x + 33.12,16,17. 34.9.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho-ke ngicela, uba ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, ake ungazise indlela yakho\x + Hlab.25.4. 119.33.\x*, ukuze ngikwazi, ukuze ngithole umusa emehlweni akho; ukhumbule futhi ukuthi lesisizwe singabantu bakho\x + Dute. 9.29. Jow. 2.17.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesithi: Ubukhona bami buzahamba \add lawe\x + 40.34-38. Isa. 63.9.\x*\add*, ngikuphumuze\x + Dute. 3.20. Josh. 21.44. 22.4. 23.1. Hlab. 95.11.\x*.
\v 15 Wasesithi kuye: Uba ubukhona bakho bungahambi \add lami\add*, ungasenyusi lapha\x + 33.1,2,3.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba kuzakwaziwa-ke ngani ukuthi ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, mina labantu bakho? Kakusikho yini ekuhambeni kwakho lathi\x + Nani 14.14.\x*? Ngakho sizakwehlukaniswa\x + 1 Kho. 8.53.\x*, mina labantu bakho, kubo bonke abantu abasebusweni bomhlaba.
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Lale into oyitshoyo ngizayenza, ngoba uthole umusa emehlweni ami\x + 33.13.\x*, njalo ngiyakwazi ngebizo\x + 33.12.\x*.
\v 18 Wasesithi: Ake ungitshengise inkazimulo yakho\x + 33.20.\x*.
\v 19 Yasisithi: Mina ngizadlulisa bonke ubuhle bami phambi kwakho\x + Hlab. 31.19. Jer. 31.14. 34.5-7.\x*, ngimemezele ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kwakho. Ngizahawukela lowo engizamhawukela, ngibe\x + Roma 9.15.\x* lomusa kulowo engizakuba lomusa kuye\x + Roma 4.4. 9.16,18.\x*.
\v 20 Yathi futhi: Ungebone ubuso bami; ngoba kakho umuntu ongangibona, aphile\x + Gen. 32.30. Dute. 5.24. Hlu. 6.22,23. 13.22. Isa. 6.5. Isam. 1.16,17. 24.10.\x*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Khangela, kulendawo ngakimi lapho ozakuma khona edwaleni;
\v 22 kuzakuthi-ke lapho inkazimulo yami isedlula, ngizakufaka esikhexeni sedwala,\x + Isa. 2.21.\x* ngikusibekele ngesandla sami ngize ngidlule\x + Hlab. 91.4.\x*;
\v 23 besengisusa isandla sami ubusubona ingemuva yami; kodwa ubuso bami kabuyikubonwa\x + 33.20. Joha. 1.18. 1 Tim. 6.16. 1 Joha. 4.12.\x*.